

This directory contains a V34-V39 compatible AmigaGuide, amigaguide.library,
and WDisplay which may be distributed by developers who have a Workbench
License and an AmigaGuide Amendment.

Note that the most of the other Readmes with these materials may use
SYS:Utilities/AmigaGuide as their default tool.  The InstallAmigaGuide
icon will install AmigaGuide on your system.  If you have a newer version
of any file or program, that file or program will not be installed.


Note - there are development drawers and files here which have no icons.


